text: Valentin Prades (born 26 September 1992) is a French modern pentathlete. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's event. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:French male modern pentathletes Category:Sportspeople from Cannes Category:Olympic modern pentathletes of France Category:Modern pentathletes at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Modern pentathletes at the 2010 Summer Youth Olympics Category:World Modern Pentathlon Championships medalists
